overview: Kim is expelled from his eighth school and finds himself at Volcano High where students fight to possess a treasured ancient document. Kim, who must resist from using his Chi, is caught in the middle.
tagline: Who is the Best WaSanGo Martial Arts Expert?
cast: Jang Hyuk|Shin Min-a|Kim Hyeong-jong|Byun Hee-bong|Heo Joon-ho
